-- Source: SELECT-6 (Vetted Queries)
SELECT
  sc.iram_publisher_id,
  sc.ircm_campaign_id,
  iot.credit_group
FROM ircm_signedcontract sc
LEFT JOIN ircm_ioterms iot ON iot.id = sc.ircm_ioterms_id
WHERE sc.iram_publisher_id = '2801605'
  AND sc.ircm_campaign_id = '<campaign_id>'
  AND sc.date_contract_end IS NULL;


-- Source: SELECT-8 (Vetted Queries)
SELECT *
FROM ircm_pendingcontract pc
INNER JOIN ircm_campaign ic ON ic.id = pc.ircm_campaign_id
WHERE pc.iram_publisher_id = '2801605';

-- reporting.publisher_matchmaking_by_campaign
SELECT campaign_id,
       is_aor,
       is_hidden_in_marketplace,
       marketplace_launch_date
FROM reporting.publisher_matchmaking_by_campaign
WHERE campaign_id IN (43843, 41541, 40805, 38211);


-- Data Warehouse
select hold_clearing
from finance_account
where account_id = 6616432;
